<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-11-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="585" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d585">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">711.61/343a</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to the Soviet Commissar for Foreign
                                    Affairs (<persName type="to">Litvinov</persName>)</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-11-16">November 16,
                                        1933</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Litvinov</hi>: I am very happy to
                                inform you that as a result of our conversations the Government of
                                the United States has decided to establish normal diplomatic
                                relations with the Government of the Union of Soviet Socialist
                                Republics and to exchange ambassadors.</p>
                            <p>I trust that the relations now established between our peoples may
                                forever remain normal and friendly, and that our nations henceforth
                                may cooperate for their mutual benefit and for the preservation of
                                the peace of the world.</p>
                            <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Franklin D. Roosevelt</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>